org.anchoranalysis.image.voxel.buffer.primitive

Class UnsignedBufferAsInt

  • Object
    • UnsignedBuffer
      • UnsignedBufferAsInt
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    UnsignedByteBuffer, UnsignedShortBuffer

    public abstract class UnsignedBufferAsInt
extends UnsignedBuffer
    A UnsignedBuffer that exposes its internal types as int.

    This means that an int is returned by getUnsigned and accepted by putUnsigned and related functions.

    Author:
    Owen Feehan
